    excerpt: "MetaMask doesn't connect to Binance Smart Chain by default. Here's the 3-minute setup that unlocks the whole BSC ecosystem.",
    content: `# Setting Up MetaMask For BSC (Complete Guide)\n\nMetaMask is the most-used crypto wallet. By default, it connects only to Ethereum. To use Turbo Loop (or anything on Binance Smart Chain), you need to add BSC as a network. It takes 3 minutes.\n\n## Step 1: Install MetaMask\n\nGo to [metamask.io](https://metamask.io). Download the extension (Chrome, Brave, Firefox) or the mobile app (iOS, Android). During setup:\n\n- Write down your 12-word seed phrase — **on paper**, not a screenshot.\n- Store it in two secure physical locations.\n- Never share it with anyone. MetaMask support will never ask for it. Turbo Loop will never ask for it. Nobody legitimate will ever ask for it.\n\n## Step 2: Add the BSC network\n\nOpen MetaMask → click the network dropdown at the top (usually says "Ethereum Mainnet"). Click **Add Network** → **Add a network manually**. Enter these exact values:\n\n- **Network Name**: Smart Chain\n- **New RPC URL**: https://bsc-dataseed.binance.org/\n- **Chain ID**: 56\n- **Currency Symbol**: BNB\n- **Block Explorer URL**: https://bscscan.com\n\nClick **Save**. You'll now see "Smart Chain" in the network dropdown.\n\n## Step 3: Switch to Smart Chain\n\nSelect Smart Chain from the network dropdown. Your MetaMask is now connected to BSC. The address is the same as your Ethereum address — MetaMask uses one wallet for all EVM chains.\n\n## Step 4: Get some BNB for gas\n\nYou need a tiny bit of BNB (Binance Coin) to pay for transactions on BSC. $5-$10 is more than enough for months of active use.\n\nOptions:\n\n- Buy through Turbo Buy (MoonPay) — select BNB, send to your wallet address.\n- Buy BNB on Binance/Coinbase/Kraken and withdraw to your wallet (make sure to select the BSC / BEP-20 network when withdrawing — **not Ethereum**).\n- Swap other tokens for BNB on PancakeSwap if you already have them on BSC.\n\n## Step 5: Connect to Turbo Loop\n\nGo to [turboloop.io](https://turboloop.io). Click **Launch App** → **Connect Wallet** → **MetaMask**. Approve the connection. You're in.\n\n## Security reminders\n\n- Never enter your seed phrase on a website. Never.\n- Bookmark the real Turbo Loop URL to avoid phishing links.\n- Disconnect your wallet from sites you're done using (MetaMask → Connected Sites).\n- Consider a hardware wallet (Ledger/Trezor) for large positions.\n\n## Mobile tip\n\nFor mobile use, MetaMask mobile has a built-in browser. Open the Turbo Loop URL within the MetaMask browser for a seamless connection experience. Trust Wallet works identically if you prefer that wallet.`,
