    content: `# The Turbo Loop Roadmap: Where We Are And Where We're Going\n\nNine phases. Six complete. Three ahead. Here's the honest status of where Turbo Loop is, what's been delivered, and what's coming.\n\n## ✅ Phase 1: Smart Contract Development (Complete)\n\nCore protocol coded — yield logic, referral tree, leadership tiers, Re-Loop, reward distribution. Solidity audited before deployment. Extensive testnet phase.\n\n## ✅ Phase 2: Security Audits (Complete)\n\nIndependent third-party audit. Findings addressed. Final report public. Zero critical issues. No known vulnerabilities.\n\n## ✅ Phase 3: Contract Renouncement + LP Lock (Complete)\n\nOwnership renounced to zero address. LP tokens time-locked. Contract is immutable forever.\n\n## ✅ Phase 4: Platform Launch (Complete)\n\nTurbo Buy (MoonPay integration) live. Turbo Swap DEX deployed. Main app at turboloop.io stable and fully operational.\n\n## ✅ Phase 5: Community Building (Complete)\n\n50+ videos across 12+ languages. Regional Telegram groups established in every major market. Daily Zoom calls ongoing. Global presence confirmed.\n\n## ✅ Phase 6: Global Public Expansion (Current)\n\nActive promotions: $100K Challenge, Creator Star program, Zoom Presenter stipend, Onboarding Bonus. Growth across 6+ continents. This is the phase we're in now — scaling from tens of thousands of users to hundreds of thousands.\n\n## 🔜 Phase 7: Mobile App\n\nNative iOS and Android apps. Features: push notifications, biometric auth, optimized mobile UI, offline dashboard. **Target**: 2026 Q3-Q4.\n\n## 🔜 Phase 8: Cross-Chain Expansion\n\nDeployment to additional chains, likely starting with Ethereum L2s (Arbitrum, Base) for low-fee Ethereum users. Unified dashboard across all chains. **Target**: 2027 Q1-Q2.\n\n## 🔜 Phase 9: DAO Governance\n\nTransition to community-driven decision-making. Proposals, voting, treasury management — all on-chain. **Target**: 2027 Q3+.\n\n## Why phases take time\n\nWe could launch a mobile app in 3 months. We won't. We could deploy cross-chain in 6 weeks. We won't. Each phase ships when it's right, when it's secure, when it's polished. The same philosophy that produced a renounced, locked, audited, trustless protocol on BSC is the same philosophy that ships future phases.\n\nNo hype. No promises we can't keep. Just steady execution, month after month. If you're here for the long run, this is how it gets built.`,
